Package: DivComAnalyses
Title: Community Analysis and visualisation using R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Florentin",
           family = "CONSTANCIAS",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "florentinconstancias@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8612-384X"))
Description: Based on phyloseq R package the aim of this package is to: facilitate data filtering (i.e., potential contaminants identified using decontam R package), help in normalizing data (i.e., 16S qPCR normalization), generate phylogenetic and taxonomic alpha-diversity metrics, visualize community composition and structure using ordination, facilitate statistical analysis based on DEseq2, ALDex, vegan R packages.
